29 section;
30 (3) Have the Educational Commission for
31 Foreign Medical Graduates evaluate his or her medical credentials;
32 (4) Hold an active, valid certificate
33 issued by the Educational Commission for Foreign Medical Graduates; and
34 (5) Pass the examination used by the
35 Educational Commission for Foreign Medical Graduates.
