4 (5) A physician who obtains a license to practice medicine in
5 the State of Arkansas shall comply with the Arkansas Medical Practices Act, §
6 17-95-201 et seq., § 17-95-301 et seq., and § 17-95-401 et seq., and all
7 rules of the Arkansas State Medical Board.
